version_description: Every version doesn't have the original tuning, and there are some mistakes in.
Contrary to the versions present in UG, this one has the clinging note (and chord) on the second "me" in the chorus.
Just a simple chord overview for this song, so anyone can play it. Just listen to the acoustic version to hear how to play the chords.
